    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-08-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-08-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="707"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d707">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Baron
                            <persName type="to">Ketteler</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-08-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 3, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Referring to Mr. Adee’s note of August 1, regarding appointment of Mr. Ide as
                    chief justice of Samoa, I beg to refer also to your legation’s note of July 8,
                    and to say that this Government concurs in the appointment of Mr. Schmidt as
                    president of council.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. Q. Gresham.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
